game.name: Princess Vs Villains Selfie Contest
game.description:
All princesses have already occupied a good space on atmegame.com. These princesses are more popular here than the deadly villains are. We have again brought to you a brand new dressing game where you girls will have a chance to meet with lovely Disney princesses and Disney Villains. Now it is up to you that which team you choose and guide her to create a perfect outfit design. Join Princess Vs Villains Selfie Contest and help your team to win this highly challenging and exciting selfie challenge!
Your three popular princesses Ariel, Anna and Rapunzel are ready to post their image on their instagram account and participate in this popular selfie contest. From the Villians hands, Hans, Ursula and Mother Gothel have given their names. Your job in this free online html5 dress-up game is to help both princesses and villains to pick up the nice outfits. Once they all collect their dresses, make sure to help them to take the coolest selfies. Do not forget to see which team will secure more likes in the end. 
There are countless outfit designs, hairstyles and jewelries to choose from. Try to give each girl a coolest facial expression in this one of best princess dress-up games for kids! Practice your best fashion designer skills to make all princesses ready for the lovely selfie contest! Prepare them for the most awaited party and help them get ready for the winner! All the best to try out more free dressing challenges on our website, no download required!
